Providing recurring monthly payments is the most direct and efficient mechanism for delivering economic relief to working families and those most vulnerable in the COVID-19 crisis.

@SenSanders, @SenKamalaHarris, and I are calling for $2k monthly payments.
https://t.co/2jegYQOe5r

RT @LCVoters: Stop what you're doing and watch this.

@SenMarkey to @EPAAWheeler:
You should be ashamed of yourself. Your agency should be…

A single check is not sufficient for households that are struggling during #COVID19. Americans need more than just one payment

@SenKamalaHarris, @SenSanders, and I are calling for a monthly $2,000 check for every individual with an income below $120,000.
